    <h5>Gameplay</h5>
    <p>Upon starting the game, questions will be loaded from an external API that is connected to an online trivia question database. The player will be given 10 seconds to answer the questin by tapping the RFID cards to the respective answer. Once
      the player proceeds to the next question, the connection to the API will be refreshed and a new set of randomised question will be loaded.</p>
