    <p>During the prototype testing, a total of 6 individuals took part in the test. Several interesting key findings were:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Having a limited sets of question would be preferable rather than the infinite amount of questions being generated with no ‘game over’.</li>
      <li>Provide option to set difficulties as some players found that the questions given were somewhat difficult.</li>
